{
  "texts": [
    "Audio files for items can either be uploaded or automatically generated.",
    "For this functionality, we are using the text-to-speech service from Amazon Web Services (AWS) 1.",
    "Lastly, a note can be added to describe an item.",
    "Settings Test creators can control all settings related to a test by overriding the default settings of tests with their own values.",
    "For example, they can control the duration of the recording of responses by test takers, whether belief statement checks are shown after items are shown, and more."
  ]
}